BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:BGGHa6Edr4RN3edqO_3RL
SUMMARY:Unexpected Productions: Seattle Theatresports Improv
DTSTAMP:20260321T020251Z
DTSTART:20260321T043000Z
DESCRIPTION:Fridays & Saturdays from 9:30pm - 11pm Seattle’s high-energy im
	prov battle where your suggestions shape every scene. Fast\, funny\, unpre
	dictable comedy Fri. & Sat. 9:30 Welcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comed
	y show\, a high-energy\, no-rules showdown where your ideas shape every sc
	ene. Seattle Theatresports at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater in Pi
	ke Place Market is part comedy battle\, part game night\, and completely p
	owered by the crowd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race and laugh til
	 it hurts! Every show\, two teams of top Seattle improvisers go head to he
	ad\, performing games\, stories\, characters\, and scenes inspired entirel
	y by your suggestions. Judges score the rounds\, decide the winners\, and 
	shape the fun (as we boo them). No scripts. No safety nets. Just fast thin
	king\, bold choices\, and pure creative mayhem. This isn’t your parents’ i
	mprov show\, unless your parents were super cool. Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://w
	ww.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/seattle-theatresports-improv/?occur
	rence=2026-03-20\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/seattle-theatresports-i
	mprov/?occurrence=2026-03-20
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:KIM8zE55vR0hAUQJxMR4E
SUMMARY:Motorcycle Riding Experience with Cascade Motorcycle Safety
DTSTAMP:20260321T020251Z
DTSTART:20260321T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Want to ride a motorcycle but don’t know where to start? Join C
	ascade Motorcycle Safety and Ride With Us for a chance to experience ridin
	g a motorcycle for free\\\, with professional Cascade Motorcycle Safety Ri
	derCoaches helping you through each step. These 1-on-1\\\, 20-minute sessi
	ons are designed for total beginners\\\, with bikes and helmets provided. 
	\\nThis program is presented with the support of Cascade Motorcycle Safety
	. \\nRide out the remainder of the day in MOHAI to see Kickstands Up! 125 
	Years of Motorcycling in the PNW. Program participants will receive a coup
	on for $5 off museum admission. \\nAs of 2/18/26\\\, the location and time
	 of this event has changed.\n\nhttps://mohai.org/event/motorcycle-riding-e
	xperience-with-cascade-motorcycle-safety/\n\nFrom MOHAI - Museum of Histor
	y & Industry
URL:https://mohai.org/event/motorcycle-riding-experience-with-cascade-motor
	cycle-safety/
LOCATION:South Seattle College North Parking Lot\\\, 6000 16th Ave SW\\\, S
	eattle\\\, WA\\\, 98106\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:mohai
CATEGORIES:MOHAI - Museum of History & Industry
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
